#: ../../introduction.md:356
msgid "By its decision 15/COP.13, the COP approved a four-year frequency for national reporting (Table 6)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../introduction.md:358
msgid "During the 2018 reporting process, Parties reported data and information for the period 2000–2015, which serves as the baseline for SDG indicator 15.3.1 and its sub-indicators. After this initial reporting, Parties continue to report the status of land condition and the SDG indicator 15.3.1 every four years, thereby increasing the reporting periods in four-year increments."
