msgid "Figure 1 shows that the first reporting period (Period 1) completed in 2022, covered the timeframe from January 1st, 2016, to December 31st, 2019. The results of the Period 1 assessment included the estimation of the proportion of degraded land (SDG Indicator 15.3.1) for 2019 (t1). Subsequent reports will reflect the land condition at the end of 2023 (t2), 2027 (t3) and, potentially, 2031 (t4), integrating changes that have occurred since the end of the baseline period (from January 1st, 2016). Therefore the reporting is incremental in time, each reporting period incorporating four additional years compared to the previous one."
